	<message label="015_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你在做什么呀？</message>
	<message label="015_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像很费劲</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我这个人一旦对某样东西讲究起来，<delay20 />
