	<message label="016_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你在做什么呀？</message>
	<message label="016_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样啊</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想要改造一下<delay8 />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然可能看起来挺复杂的，<delay20 />
但一般来说<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要有足够的耐心和毅力，
大多都不是什么难事啊。<pageBreak />最近好像有些人给这行为取了个名字叫DIY，
听起来挺新潮的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过我还是更习惯称之为手工活啊！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要不要也试做做看
我构想的<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />来吧，很简单的，别担心。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我想做做看！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不用了</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样啊，<delay8 />那我就继续忙活啦。<delay frames="40" />
收尾工作还没做完呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯？<delay8 />难道说<delay8 />你也知道
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />的
