	<message label="008_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我知道哦！</message>
	<message label="008_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我以前有做过哦！</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />噢，<delay8 />这样啊！<delay20 />
真不愧是<tag a="110" b="3" />你啊！</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我本来是想这样的，<delay20 />
但你已经拿不下东西了啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等你能拿东西了再告诉我一声吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好啊！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />制作方法写在这笔记里了，<delay8 />
按照这个做的话，应该能漂亮地做出来。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我觉得做这个并没有那么难，<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="3" />你来做的话，
应该是小事一桩吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个手册，<delay20 />
可以的话，
你能拿去给别人看看吗？
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我把手册的笔记<delay8 />给你，<delay frames="30" />
因为难得记下来了，
我想让大家都试着做一次。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />
成了一大热潮的话<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就是拾火鼓风的其中一人。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">说起来，<delay20 />我是不是还没把
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />的手册
交给你啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我把制作方法完完整整地写在这里了，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要小心别弄丢它哦。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要有南瓜才能制作这个哦。<delay frames="40" />
如果用自己种出来的南瓜来制作，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没准能做出一件品质格外好的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听说，如果要改造它的话，<delay20 />
不能使用普通的南瓜，<delay8 />
得用颜色不同的南瓜才行。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要种植足够多的南瓜，<delay8 />
到时候就会有不同颜色的长出来。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总之，多种一些总会碰到的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="032" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔，<delay8 />我等了你一会儿了。<delay frames="40" />
你是过来拿<delay8 />
刚才没能交给你的东西的吧？</message>
	<message label="033" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />嗯？<delay frames="40" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你好像<delay8 />
已经知道<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />的
制作方法了啊。</message>
	<message label="034" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样的话，<delay8 />你就不需要这份手册了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也谈不上是替代品啦，<delay20 />
我分你一些能用作材料的<colour id="1" />南瓜<colour id="65535" />吧。</message>
	<message label="035" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">现在正好是万圣节时期，<delay20 />
用这<colour id="1" />南瓜<colour id="65535" />做件好东西，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把岛上装饰得漂漂亮亮的吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="036" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">既然这样，<delay8 />这手册你就不需要了吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过我也不好意思让你空手而归，<delay20 />
有没有什么能让你带走的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了，<delay8 />我正好有件好东西！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是<colour id="1" />糖果<colour id="65535" />哦！<delay frames="30" />我把它给你了。<delay frames="40" />
